<%# About me %>
<div id="about" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center mt-10 p-5 md:px-40 md:m-20 border-b border-gray-200 pb-20">
  <%= image_tag("marcus.jpg", class: "ml-auto w-80 mx-auto mt-auto rounded shadow-xl") %>

  <div class="mt-10 ml-5 md:ml-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl w-full flex justify-center mb-10 text-blue-400">About Me</h1>
    <p>I am 25 years old from a small town in North Devon called Barnstaple. I attended Petroc College where i obtained a BTEC in Furniture Making, moving forward i took a job in Groundworks but ultimately decided it wasn't going to be a career. Finally finding computer programming at the age of 24, i decided to take a course at Le Wagon... now i'm looking for my first role.</p>
    <p class="mt-5">I truly enjoy web/software development and love to work around the challenges it presents and I am always keen to learn more. I possess a clear, logical mind with a practical approach to problem solving and a drive to see things through to completion. I have a good eye for details and always ensure my work is accurate.</p>

    <div class="flex space-y-2 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-5 mt-10 flex-col md:flex-row">
      <a href="#contact" class="border border-gray-300 px-10 py-2 uppercase w-max rounded shadow-md hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white transition duration-300">Contact Me</a>
      <a href="#portfolio" class="border border-gray-300 px-10 py-2 uppercase w-max rounded shadow-md hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white transition duration-300">See Portfolio</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# Projects %>
